---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../content/site.ts';

const title = `Privacy Policy | ${siteConfig.name}`;
const description = 'Privacy Policy for Solvin IT — how we collect, use, and protect your information.';
const effectiveDate = 'May 19, 2026';
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description} noIndex={false}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">

      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="heading-1 text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Effective date: {effectiveDate}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose-legal">

        <p>
          This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Solvin IT</strong> ("we," "us," or "our"), operated by Jose Fernando Gonzales, collects, uses, and protects information when you visit <a href={siteConfig.url}>{siteConfig.url}</a> (the "Site") or use any services or products we provide.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>Information you provide directly</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact form submissions</strong> — name, email address, subject, and message body when you reach out through our contact page.</li>
          <li><strong>AI chatbot interactions</strong> — questions and messages you send to the "Fred" AI Butler widget during a session.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Theme preference</strong> — stored in your browser's <code>localStorage</code> to remember your dark/light mode choice. This data never leaves your device.</li>
          <li><strong>Standard server logs</strong> — GitHub Pages may collect standard web-server logs (IP address, browser type, referring URL, page visited, timestamp) as part of hosting infrastructure. We do not control or have access to these logs.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your enquiries and messages submitted through the contact form.</li>
          <li>To provide real-time responses from the AI Butler chatbot during your current session.</li>
          <li>To maintain your preferred display theme across page loads.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>The Site relies on the following third-party services, each with their own privacy practices:</p>

        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Service</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Privacy Policy</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>GitHub Pages</td>
              <td>Website hosting</td>
              <td><a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Privacy Statement</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Formspree</td>
              <td>Contact form processing</td>
              <td><a href="https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Formspree Privacy Policy</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Google reCAPTCHA v3</td>
              <td>Spam prevention on contact form</td>
              <td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Google Fonts</td>
              <td>Typography (Inter, Playfair Display, DM Mono)</td>
              <td><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>RAG on Me API (<code>rag-on-me.solvin.co</code>)</td>
              <td>AI chatbot responses</td>
              <td>Operated by Solvin IT — see section 4 below</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2>4. AI Chatbot Data</h2>
        <p>
          The "Fred" AI Butler sends your messages to our backend API (<code>rag-on-me.solvin.co</code>) solely to generate a response. Messages are processed in real time and are <strong>not stored permanently</strong> after your session ends. A temporary <code>thread_id</code> is generated per conversation to maintain context within a single session; this identifier is not linked to your identity and is discarded after the session.
        </p>
        <p>Do not submit sensitive personal or financial information through the chatbot.</p>

        <h2>5. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
        <p>
          We do not use advertising cookies or tracking cookies. The Site uses browser <code>localStorage</code> only to persist your theme preference (<code>theme</code> key). No cookies are set by our first-party code. Third-party services listed above may set their own cookies subject to their respective policies.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact form messages</strong> are retained by Formspree according to their data retention policy and by us only as long as necessary to respond to your enquiry.</li>
          <li><strong>Chatbot session data</strong> is not retained after the session ends.</li>
          <li><strong>Theme preference</strong> persists in your browser until you clear site data.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of personal information we hold about you. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at the address below. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
        <p>Philippine residents may also refer to the <strong>Data Privacy Act of 2012 (Republic Act No. 10173)</strong> for applicable rights.</p>

        <h2>8. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take reasonable technical measures to protect information in transit (HTTPS) and limit data collection to what is strictly necessary. No method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure; we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>The Site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has submitted information through our Site, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.</p>

        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Effective date" at the top of this page will reflect the most recent revision. Continued use of the Site after an update constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy can be directed to:<br />
          <strong>Jose Fernando Gonzales — Solvin IT</strong><br />
          Makati City, Philippines<br />
          <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.author.email}`}>{siteConfig.author.email}</a>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .prose-legal {
    @apply text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-6;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    @apply text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-3;
  }
  .prose-legal h3 {
    @apply text-base font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-2;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    @apply text-base;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    @apply list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2 text-base;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    @apply text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-primary-800 dark:hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors;
  }
  .prose-legal code {
    @apply font-mono text-sm bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    @apply font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white;
  }
  .prose-legal table {
    @apply w-full text-sm border-collapse mt-4;
  }
  .prose-legal th {
    @apply text-left font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-2 pr-4;
  }
  .prose-legal td {
    @apply border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 py-2 pr-4 align-top;
  }
</style>
